README.md
     1Рєњ# humanize
    12РєњThis modest package contains various common humanization utilities, like turning a
    13Рєњnumber into a fuzzy human-readable duration ("3 minutes ago") or into a human-readable
    14Рєњsize or throughput. It is localized to:
    15Рєњ
    16Рєњ- Arabic
    17Рєњ- Basque
    18Рєњ- Bengali
    19Рєњ- Brazilian Portuguese
    20Рєњ- Catalan
    21Рєњ- Danish
    22Рєњ- Dutch
    23Рєњ- Esperanto
    24Рєњ- European Portuguese
    25Рєњ- Finnish
    26Рєњ- French
    27Рєњ- German
    28Рєњ- Greek
    29Рєњ- Hebrew
    30Рєњ- Indonesian
    31Рєњ- Italian
    32Рєњ- Japanese
    33Рєњ- Klingon
    34Рєњ- Korean
    35Рєњ- Norwegian
    36Рєњ- Persian
    37Рєњ- Polish
    38Рєњ- Russian
      РєњРђд
